<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Food and Recipe Sharing</title>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Header -->
  <header>
    <h1>Welcome to Dish Hunt's Food and Recipe Sharing</h1>
    <p>Create an account and start saving your favorite recipes!</p>
  </header>

  <!-- Categories  -->
  <section>
    <h2>Categories</h2>
    <div class="category-links">
      {{#each categories}}
        <a href="{{link}}"><img src="{{image}}" alt="{{name}}"></a>
      {{/each}}
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Introduction -->
   <div class="welcome-message">
      <h1>Hello and Welcome to Dish Hunt!</h1>
      <p>
        At Dish Hunt, we're all about sharing the love for food and recipes with our amazing community of foodies. Whether you're a seasoned chef or a cooking enthusiast, you're in the right place!
      </p>
      <p>
        Don't have an account yet? Sign up now to unlock a world of benefits! With a Dish Hunt account, you can save and share your favorite recipes, follow other foodies, and be part of the culinary conversation by leaving comments on recipes you try.
      </p>
      <p>
        So why wait? Let's embark on a mouthwatering journey together! Feel free to explore and search our vast collection of delicious recipes, and let the culinary adventure begin!
      </p>
      <p class="cta-message">Ready to get started? Join Dish Hunt now and let the flavors unite!</p>
      <a href="#" class="signup-cta">Sign Up Now!</a>
    </div>
  </main>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2023 Dish Hunt. All rights reserved. ðŸ˜‰</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
